hub.com/users/kabum/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kabum/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-16t21:32:48z","updated_at":"2013-09-16t21:32:48z","body":"i just get results for folders. not for files (the result box just isn't shown. the highlighting for the current folder works."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24570981","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/4263#issuecomment-24570981","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4263","id":24570981,"user":{"login":"petemcfarlane","id":3472717,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e8e19e98d7fce9603dc608557993ad0f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f9f19e0b9b727c88f7e126b5f33887118.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e8e19e98d7fce9603dc608557993ad0f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane","html_url":"https://github.com/petemcfarlane","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-17t08:15:57z","updated_at":"2013-09-17t08:15:57z","body":"issue - pressing return sometimes opens / downloads search result when not intended.\r\nsteps to reproduce:\r\ntype something in search bar, use the arrow keys to highlight a result, then click the 'new' button, choose file or folder, type any name and press return. this should create a new file/folder. instead it downloads/opens whatever file/folder is 'selected' in the search results box.\r\n\r\nideally, when a user clicks outside the search results box, all the results should empty and the search input should un-focus. \r\n\r\nissue 2, as @kabum commented, it's very misleading to show a folder icon for results which are files. \r\n\r\ni think the icon should be shown before the user has to hover, as it isn't shown if the user uses the arrow keys, and nothing is gained by hiding it - it's just another useful visual cue to have all the time - is it a file / folder / contacts / event etc. \r\n\r\nalso, choosing a file result, by click or enter, should show the file in it's location in the web browser, not directly open/download it.\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24574701","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/4263#issuecomment-24574701","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4263","id":24574701,"user":{"login":"butonic","id":956847,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9760c134cabf66e10dbba06d7525f5c7?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f92925ec1ad893739ed57986f18e2f060.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"9760c134cabf66e10dbba06d7525f5c7","url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic","html_url":"https://github.com/butonic","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-17t09:25:16z","updated_at":"2013-09-17t09:25:16z","body":"actually clicking on the folder icon will open the folder containing the file, scroll to it and hightlight it. kind of a 'navigate' action only available for files & folder results. that the current default action for files is 'download' is a ux nightmare because you will not be able to search a file and then share it. in the future we are planning to:\r\n1. limit search result to types related to the current app.\r\n2. filter what is visible rather than showing a search box.\r\n3. hide the search input field iin apps that don't have a search provider. \r\n4. add a dedicated search app that allows searching over all content.\r\nthis pr is just an intermediate step to make search results more useful.\r\n\r\n@kabum do you have versioning, encryption or trashbin enabled? or were you just confused about the folder icon? i do get file results.\r\n\r\n@petemcfarlane will look into the enter bug today.\r\n\r\nimo we should make the 'navigate' action the default and remove the download option. when you are searching for a file you might want to do something else than downloading it. like sharing or open it in pictures / music."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24575337","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/4263#issuecomment-24575337","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4263","id":24575337,"user":{"login":"petemcfarlane","id":3472717,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e8e19e98d7fce9603dc608557993ad0f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f9f19e0b9b727c88f7e126b5f33887118.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e8e19e98d7fce9603dc608557993ad0f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane","html_url":"https://github.com/petemcfarlane","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/petemcfarlane/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-17t09:38:04z","updated_at":"2013-09-17t09:38:04z","body":"yes, definitely make the 'navigate' action default, it is unintuitive that you have to click the folder/file icon (which does work nicely might i add).\r\n\r\nif and when the search bar is limited only to the current app, could it be made clear, possibly with a placeholder, e.g. 'search files & folders', or 'search contacts' and maybe the last option could be 'search in all apps >>' which would copy the query across to the new dedicated search app?"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24576319","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/4263#issuecomment-24576319","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4263","id":24576319,"user":{"login":"butonic","id":956847,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9760c134cabf66e10dbba06d7525f5c7?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f92925ec1ad893739ed57986f18e2f060.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"9760c134cabf66e10dbba06d7525f5c7","url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic","html_url":"https://github.com/butonic","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/